(My Beloved Father Qiu Nianyuan)

21
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:26,470
Dad,

22
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:28,270
believe me,

23
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:32,590
I will avenge the Qiu and the Li families,

24
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,870
and realize your dream
of saving our nation.

25
00:02:45,780 --> 00:02:49,700
(Longxi Hall)

26
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,400
(Mr. Qiu,)

27
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:00,470
(I know, for who I am)

28
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:01,470
(I shouldn't even be here,)

29
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,360
(but I guarantee)

30
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:05,750
(that as long as I can,)

31
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:08,680
(I will take good care of Yue)

32
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,910
(and help her achieve her goals)

33
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:13,150
(until I am no longer needed.)

34
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:34,280
Where are Du's men?

35
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,520
They have been driven out.

36
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,400
When did you do it?

37
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:46,960
Why didn't you tell me?

38
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:49,520
The Armory is now yours.

39
00:03:50,570 --> 00:03:52,840
Both Xiao Li and Du Hanqing

40
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:54,790
will hold you in respect,

41
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,630
including my foster father.

42
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,680
In Jiangcheng,

43
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:00,590
no one will dare to threaten you.

44
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,030
Mine?

45
00:04:04,310 --> 00:04:05,840
I'm only managing it
for you for the time being.

46
00:04:06,050 --> 00:04:06,960
Now that you have returned

47
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,030
and are in good shape,

48
00:04:08,150 --> 00:04:09,990
the Northern Division should
be handed over back to you.

49
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:13,840
You are more suitable for it.

50
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,630
Why me?

51
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,600
Because all the other people
have their own interest,

52
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,600
nobody is like you

53
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:23,160
or your father

54
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,000
who worked whole-heartedly

55
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,350
for the interest of Jiangcheng civilians.

56
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:30,110
What about you?

57
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:32,230
Me?

58
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,760
I have mine as well.

59
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:36,920
What is that?

60
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,830
My interest is

61
00:04:40,430 --> 00:04:41,270
you.

62
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,040
Also, the Armory

63
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,390
was originally the Qiu family's asset.

64
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:50,560
You are the rightful owner.

65
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,040
Dad, tea for you.

66
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:07,840
Dad,

67
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:08,950
why must we

68
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:10,310
establish a machinery factory

69
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,830
to do business with foreigners?

70
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:13,480
Because in the modern age,

71
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:16,560
the Westerners
own the advanced technologies.

72
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:20,160
If we wish to develop,

73
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,870
we must first learn.

74
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,310
Like what Mr. Wei Yuan said.

75
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:28,800
"Learn from foreigners to beat them."

76
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:30,590
Ruoran,

77
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:34,360
I hope you return soon

78
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:37,160
and help me run the factory.

79
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,560
Unfortunately,

80
00:05:43,190 --> 00:05:45,070
Dad didn't achieve his goal,

81
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:48,270
instead, our family was ruined.

82
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,640
And this place

83
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,950
has become the target

84
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:55,000
of all those warlords.

85
00:05:56,870 --> 00:05:58,920
I actually agree with Mr. Qiu.

86
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,270
However, in this day,

87
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,270
a peaceful and stable life

88
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:06,680
has become wishing thinking.

89
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:13,470
Yanting,

90
00:06:14,830 --> 00:06:16,800
we may pick up your previous plan

91
00:06:17,390 --> 00:06:18,630
and provide arms for everyone.

92
00:06:19,270 --> 00:06:20,430
When the war is over,

93
00:06:21,310 --> 00:06:23,070
we'll convert it
into a machinery factory

94
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:25,270
to provide resources for everyone.

95
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,000
This way,

96
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:29,800
our life will get better and better.

97
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:33,150
OK.

98
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,560
Oh my.

99
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,640
A rare visitor.

100
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:12,040
Welcome.

101
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,320
Mr. Du,

102
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,360
