103
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:18,560
It isn't easy to meet you.

104
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:23,800
You are out of Xiao Mansion.

105
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:26,800
Which, too, is quite a change.

106
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,800
What would you like to talk to me?

107
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,360
A good deal.

108
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:46,740
(Title Deed)

109
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,390
Title dead for the Armory.

110
00:07:56,870 --> 00:07:57,950
Too bad,

111
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,360
you warlords

112
00:08:01,510 --> 00:08:03,870
keep competing over the Armory,

113
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:06,560
so even if I have this deed,

114
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:08,360
what would be the point?

115
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,000
With this deed,

116
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:16,600
you'll be the legal owner of the Armory.

117
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,760
What?

118
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:23,270
Do you plan to buy me off with this?

119
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:25,880
Mr. Du,

120
00:08:26,870 --> 00:08:27,800
I remember

121
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:29,920
you were the largest shareholder

122
00:08:30,630 --> 00:08:32,000
of the Armory initially,

123
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:34,720
but Gu Yanting took it from you

124
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:37,000
and gave it to a woman.

125
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,270
Word on Jiangcheng street

126
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:44,600
says you, as the biggest arms dealer,

127
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:47,120
couldn't even keep your own thing.

128
00:08:47,910 --> 00:08:49,630
How can you tolerate it?

129
00:08:56,510 --> 00:08:58,080
How would you like me to help you,

130
00:08:58,790 --> 00:09:01,240
so I can have the deed?

131
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:04,200
Help me rebuild my Jiangcheng Army.

132
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,870
Mum, why are dressing like this?

133
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,270
Are you feeling unwell?

134
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,120
It's you. Where's your dad?

135
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:18,000
Dad said

136
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,320
