150
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,600
Why must you personally do it?

151
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:16,960
You weren't healed,

152
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:18,080
and now you're in a worse state.

153
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:22,080
I must get back
what belongs to Yue myself.

154
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:22,990
But...

155
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,030
No but.

156
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,600
